      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Garangolm Gone Mad",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "We\u0027ve received an urgent\r\nmessage that a Garangolm is\r\ngoing berserk. If we don\u0027t do\r\nsomething soon, I\u0027m afraid\r\nsomeone might get seriously\r\ninjured or worse! Well, Hunter,\r\ncan we leave this one to you?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Garangolm foldingo",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Un Garangolm en cavale\r\nnous pose des soucis.\r\nCe monstre \u00E9norme pourrait causer\r\nbeaucoup de d\u00E9g\u00E2ts si on\r\nne l\u0027arr\u00EAte pas. Tu pourrais t\u0027en\r\ncharger, \u003CLSNR {Chasseur}{Chasseuse}\u003E ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Mostro furioso",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Pare che sia stato avvistato un\r\nGarangolm che si aggira libero. Per\r\nvia delle sue enormi dimensioni,\r\nse non lo fermiamo al pi\u00F9 presto,\r\npotrebbe causare molti danni.\r\nAllora, puoi occupartene tu?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Tobendes Monster",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Wir haben eine dringende Nach-\r\nricht erhalten, ein Garangolm\r\nw\u00FCrde durchdrehen. Wenn wir\r\nnicht etwas tun, k\u00F6nnte jemand\r\nernsthaft verletzt werden, oder\r\nSchlimmeres! \u003CLSNR {J\u00E4ger} {J\u00E4gerin}\u003E, k\u00F6nnen\r\nwir das dir \u00FCberlassen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Garangolm.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Monstruo desbocado",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Nos comunican con urgencia que\r\nhay un Garangolm suelto. Es\r\ntan grande que, como no lo\r\nparemos, lo va a destrozar\r\ntodo. Dime, \u00BFpodemos dejar\r\nesto en tus manos?",
        "Target": "Caza un Garangolm",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0411\u0443\u0448\u0443\u044E\u0449\u0438\u0439 \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440",
